step_data.thought: I've updated the quantity to 100, but I notice that the Stock Status is still set to 'Out of Stock' (bid 1137). Since I've added inventory, I should change the stock status to 'In Stock' to properly reflect the inventory update. The stock status dropdown is currently set to 'Out of Stock', so I need to change it to 'In Stock' by selecting that option from the dropdown. After that, I'll need to save the changes to complete the inventory update.
